	<DifficultyDef>
		<defName>Easy</defName>
		<label>✬ Builder</label>
		<description>Build a community with a taste of danger. Threats appear, but they're weakened.

Recommended for:

- Players who are new to this kind of game.
- Players who want to build a perfect colony.
- Players who want to relax.</description>
		<difficulty>1</difficulty>
		<threatScale>0.20</threatScale>
		<predatorsHuntHumanlikes>false</predatorsHuntHumanlikes>
		<colonistMoodOffset>10</colonistMoodOffset>
